      "committedDate": "2026-05-20T11:51:03Z",
      "messageBody": "Rename the existing core Harness implementation to HarnessLegacy while preserving the temporary Harness export alias for downstream consumers. Update legacy harness tests to use the renamed class and add the core changeset for the migration step.",
      "messageHeadline": "chore(core): rename legacy harness class",
      "oid": "3dbe86cd4655834f0f5d17fe37bef709ff1c14f9"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-05-20T11:42:20Z",
      "authors": [
        {
          "email": "mbenhamd@gmail.com",
          "id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2NzIwNDY3",
          "login": "mbenhamd",
          "name": "Mohamed BEN HAMDOUNE"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-05-20T11:52:34Z",
      "messageBody": "Add the @mastra/core/harness/v1 export and build entry as the next stacked Harness v1 migration step. Introduce minimal Harness and Session scaffold exports plus shared stable type re-exports so follow-up PRs can add the audited v1 type layer and runtime behavior.",
      "messageHeadline": "feat(core): add harness v1 subpath scaffold",
      "oid": "8c38a5009278e846759136bc348a489656b4a645"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-05-20T12:14:37Z",
      "authors": [
        {
          "email": "mbenhamd@gmail.com",
          "id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2NzIwNDY3",
          "login": "mbenhamd",
          "name": "Mohamed BEN HAMDOUNE"
        }
      ],
      "committedDate": "2026-05-20T12:33:59Z",
      "messageBody": "Add the public Harness v1 type, config, context, error, and event surface behind the existing @mastra/core/harness/v1 subpath. Keep this slice compile-only so the storage domain and runtime behavior can land in the next stacked PRs.",
      "messageHeadline": "feat(core): add harness v1 type layer",
      "oid": "7a49669dce227713bfa7c4a209ce3d3e8dc0069c"
    },
    {
      "authoredDate": "2026-05-20T13:23:34Z",
      "authors": [
